# - [x] Type bindings preserved
#
# Edge Cases:
# - [x] Empty module (returns empty sets)
# - [x] No generics (all goes to specialized)
# - [x] Only templates (specialized is empty)
# - [x] Mixed generic and non-generic
#
# Memory Safety:
